  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.poster.avif?t=1770428051\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.webm?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.mp4?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A physics sandbox simulation game for you to mess with. Build world you can imagine and destroy anything you create.<br><br>You can throw asteroid into the building, crush it, set it on fire, or smash it with bomb explosions.<br><br>Tornado, sand storm, black hole, tsunami, zombie apocalypse, nuclear explosion, and many many more!<br><br>Explore open levels or you can build your world. You can import voxel models and create your cube world. <br><br>Play, destroy, and have fun!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.poster.avif?t=1770428051\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.webm?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.mp4?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.poster.avif?t=1770428051\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.webm?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/dd4bb87bd2f3709039c9d9560af537c1.mp4?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A physics sandbox simulation game for you to mess with. Build world you can imagine and destroy anything you create.<br><br>You can throw asteroid into the building, crush it, set it on fire, or smash it with bomb explosions.<br><br>Tornado, sand storm, black hole, tsunami, zombie apocalypse, nuclear explosion, and many many more!<br><br>Explore open levels or you can build your world. You can import voxel models and create your cube world. <br><br>Play, destroy, and have fun!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.poster.avif?t=1770428051\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.webm?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1645270/extras/1ac34948f286f9ac1643b0d7bb9e81fe.mp4?t=1770428051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
